<div class="com-share" data-id="2981" data-title="《《极速前进》开播，不就是明星豪华版定向跑么》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/2981/medium/2981.gif?1436654204" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/2981" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
